&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Job Overview&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Account Director at CG Life is an essential leader and strategic client partner with 10 years of agency experience in the pharmaceutical sector. As the day-to-day business builder and strategic client advisor, this person thrives in fast-paced environments and is excited by the challenge of helping their clients obtain results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Account Director combines past experiences, an in-depth understanding of market strategies, and the client’s goals to execute marketing projects, programs, and campaigns successfully. This individual is committed to challenging the status quo and inspiring others to do the same as they lead their teams within the Client Services department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a remote-flexible role; candidates in the Eastern Time Zone are preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Responsibilities, including but not limited to:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Relationships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Builds and maintains strong business relationships by establishing trust and credibility at all levels in the client&#39;s organization, including senior management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establishes regular communication with clients to ensure their satisfaction and facilitate our long-term profitability and growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Persuades clients as a strategic partner with a perspective they can trust.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guides client planning and forward-thinking via established industry knowledge to support the agency&#39;s recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drives the growth of client accounts by identifying challenges and pursuing upsell opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborates with key leaders to present effective solutions that engage clients and generate excitement for additional projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supports new business efforts by actively participating in strategy sessions, attending pitches, and delivering presentations when appropriate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Finance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures the accurate management of the account financials, including managing reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leads and reports on monthly and quarterly forecast updates for the assigned client account(s).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Oversight&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Displays personal ownership and responsibility for the client account by handling all elements from the briefing to the scope execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leads assigned agency team to deliver for clients, ensuring all work is on strategy, on time, and on budget.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Directs, coaches, and motivates the client services team to effectively deliver for our clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership &amp;amp; Strategic Guidance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acts as the client’s champion internally and brings their point of view to our work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert on the client account, target audiences, and competitive landscape to contribute toward business solutions for their business, ensuring our solutions align with their goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successfully serves as a point of authority and/or source of advice for assigned client(s).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for brand planning, strategic and tactical deliverables, and contributing to budget planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates influence and diplomacy in written and verbal presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internal Relationships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Builds strong relationships with all functional team leads, ensuring the client’s objectives are consistently met.&lt;/li&gt;
