&lt;li&gt;Translate strategic insights into compelling visual ideas that elevate the client’s brand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with copy leads to drive cohesive creative thinking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Push creative boundaries while ensuring solutions remain strategically grounded.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on direction to designers and art directors throughout the creative process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present creative work confidently to internal stakeholders and clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
