&lt;li&gt;Model inclusive and collaborative creative leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the growth and creative culture of the department.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Operational &amp;amp; Industry Awareness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a deep understanding of visual trends, technologies, and production techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure creative adheres to pharma regulatory expectations while still delivering innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support brand planning and tactical development in partnership with cross-functional leads.&lt;/li&gt;
