&lt;li&gt;Engage with internal and external stakeholders, including executives, partners, and vendors, to communicate technical project statuses, escalate issues, and solicit feedback to inform decision-making and drive continued alignment between teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal teams and external partners and/or vendors to ensure the availability of required resources for technical service delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
