&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;gns8qe&quot; data-start=&quot;891&quot; data-end=&quot;1036&quot;&gt;Partner with Art Directors, Designers, Copywriters, and Creative Directors to execute production-ready creative assets across multiple channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;t6125c&quot; data-start=&quot;1037&quot; data-end=&quot;1173&quot;&gt;Build, resize, version, and adapt existing creative for print, digital, social, presentations, email, and other marketing deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;b3mkux&quot; data-start=&quot;1174&quot; data-end=&quot;1292&quot;&gt;Prepare accurate, press-ready and digital-ready files that meet technical specifications and production requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ah0bqy&quot; data-start=&quot;1293&quot; data-end=&quot;1405&quot;&gt;Implement revisions efficiently while maintaining design integrity, brand consistency, and attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1jsbs5m&quot; data-start=&quot;1406&quot; data-end=&quot;1519&quot;&gt;Create layouts, image retouching, graphic production, iconography, and other supporting visual assets as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;19pz0bm&quot; data-start=&quot;1520&quot; data-end=&quot;1659&quot;&gt;Design and format PowerPoint presentations that align with brand guidelines, including creating templates, graphics, charts, and diagrams&lt;/li&gt;
